               <p>EDINGTON FULTON. I live in Cumming-street, Pentonville. On the morning of the 17th of July I was in <placeName id="t18320906-112-crimeloc636">Bunhill-row</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18320906-112-crimeloc636" type="placeName" value="Bunhill-row"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18320906-112-crimeloc636" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320906-112-off634 t18320906-112-crimeloc636"></join> - a person spoke to me, and I missed my handkerchief; I saw the prisoner running, and he was stopped by the Policeman - I charged him with taking my handkerchief; he said he had not got it, but when we were going to search him, he had it secreted behind his coat - I saw it drop.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18320906-112-person1007">
                  RALPH 
                  JOHN
